Package: eneRgymaps
Type: Package
Title: Geographic maps related to the energy sector
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Francois Beaude
Maintainer: Francois Beaude <francois.beaude@gmail.com>
Description: Package allowing to display geographic maps related to the energy sector.
    Allows to map electricity information (related to e.g. countries, bidding zones, and load-frequency control areas) in Europe.
License: LGPL. External elements (e.g. shapefiles and EIC codes) are the property (and subject to the license) of their respective owners.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 2.1.0)
